00396 template <typename T>
00397 class MamaFieldCacheFieldVector
00398 {
00399 protected:
00400     MamaFieldCacheFieldVector()
00401         : mValues(NULL)
00402         , mSize(0)
00403     {
00404     }
00405     ~MamaFieldCacheFieldVector()
00406     {
00407         if (!mValues || !mSize)
00408         {
00409             return;
00410         }
00411         delete[] mValues;
00412     }
00413 
00414     void grow(mama_size_t newSize) const
00415     {
00416         if (newSize <= mSize)
00417             return;
00418 
00419         T* newVector = new T[newSize];
00420         for (mama_size_t i = 0; i < mSize; ++i)
00421         {
00422             newVector[i] = mValues[i];
00423         }
00424 
00425         if (mValues) 
00426             delete[] mValues;
00427 
00428         mValues = newVector;
00429         mSize = newSize;
00430     }
00431 
00432 protected:
00433     mutable T* mValues;
00434     mutable mama_size_t mSize;
00435 };
